  "detailed_description": "Breed the ultimate gun and struggle survive on a harsh planet!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Guns!</strong></u></h2>Have you ever wanted your shotgun and your bazooka to procreate? Do you fantacize about your sniper and your machine gun gettin down and durty? In Wyrdgun not only is this a reality... its a necessity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1038277c174bfc1486cf9b08906a643a.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1038277c174bfc1486cf9b08906a643a.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1038277c174bfc1486cf9b08906a643a.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every gun has 16 mutatable stats and can gain 32 additional special stats through breeding that greatly change the gun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Aliens!</strong></u></h2>Kill loads of freaks!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/f0beb5ec9965501404f57a20af32ca9b.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/f0beb5ec9965501404f57a20af32ca9b.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/f0beb5ec9965501404f57a20af32ca9b.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Heaps of em!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Planet!</strong></u></h2>Fight on an open world, procedurally generated, fully destructible, desert planet!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/984b4f460c905dfb443374701f852f6b.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/984b4f460c905dfb443374701f852f6b.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/984b4f460c905dfb443374701f852f6b.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Mutations!</strong></u></h2>Gain wings, grappling webs, invisibility, and more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1e20ecb31ed7f030464e901d0e995c0d.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1e20ecb31ed7f030464e901d0e995c0d.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1e20ecb31ed7f030464e901d0e995c0d.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mutations are the progression system of Wyrdgun and persist across runs!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Perks!</strong></u></h2>Wyrdgun has a modular perk system. Each perk contains a trigger and an effect. For example: hp is low => slow time, on kill => create a nova, or on dig => + digspeed!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/8e7a269eeb0a6e8f0d9e1e76c5da1be4.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/8e7a269eeb0a6e8f0d9e1e76c5da1be4.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/8e7a269eeb0a6e8f0d9e1e76c5da1be4.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are 28 triggers and 45 effects to choose from!",
  "about_the_game": "Breed the ultimate gun and struggle survive on a harsh planet!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Guns!</strong></u></h2>Have you ever wanted your shotgun and your bazooka to procreate? Do you fantacize about your sniper and your machine gun gettin down and durty? In Wyrdgun not only is this a reality... its a necessity.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1038277c174bfc1486cf9b08906a643a.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1038277c174bfc1486cf9b08906a643a.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1038277c174bfc1486cf9b08906a643a.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every gun has 16 mutatable stats and can gain 32 additional special stats through breeding that greatly change the gun!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Aliens!</strong></u></h2>Kill loads of freaks!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/f0beb5ec9965501404f57a20af32ca9b.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/f0beb5ec9965501404f57a20af32ca9b.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/f0beb5ec9965501404f57a20af32ca9b.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Heaps of em!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Planet!</strong></u></h2>Fight on an open world, procedurally generated, fully destructible, desert planet!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/984b4f460c905dfb443374701f852f6b.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/984b4f460c905dfb443374701f852f6b.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/984b4f460c905dfb443374701f852f6b.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Mutations!</strong></u></h2>Gain wings, grappling webs, invisibility, and more.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1e20ecb31ed7f030464e901d0e995c0d.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1e20ecb31ed7f030464e901d0e995c0d.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/1e20ecb31ed7f030464e901d0e995c0d.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Mutations are the progression system of Wyrdgun and persist across runs!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Perks!</strong></u></h2>Wyrdgun has a modular perk system. Each perk contains a trigger and an effect. For example: hp is low => slow time, on kill => create a nova, or on dig => + digspeed!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/8e7a269eeb0a6e8f0d9e1e76c5da1be4.poster.avif?t=1698406363\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/8e7a269eeb0a6e8f0d9e1e76c5da1be4.webm?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343000/extras/8e7a269eeb0a6e8f0d9e1e76c5da1be4.mp4?t=1698406363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are 28 triggers and 45 effects to choose from!",
